title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 5 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 5 2022
description:
Aaron Rodgers and Novak Djokovic become enemies of the left. NY Governor Hochul orders hospitals to correctly categorize covid cases. Ryan Girdusky, author of They're Not Listening: How the Elites Created the National Populist Revolution and founder of the 1776 Project PAC, joins Clay and Buck to discuss redistricting and the 2022 election. Schumer in '05: Ending filibuster would be "doomsday for democracy."
